text: Sherin Ahmed is a Bangladeshi politician who is elected as Member of 11th Jatiya Sangsad of Reserved Seats for Women. She is a politician of Bangladesh Awami League. ==References== Category:Living people Category:Awami League politicians Category:People from Dhaka District Category:11th Jatiya Sangsad members Category:Women members of the Jatiya Sangsad Category:1956 births
title: Sherin Ahmed
